Yconic Intercollegiate AI Hackathon
March 28-29th, 2026
Team: Insight Lab

Finance Buddy
=============

An AI-powered personal finance companion for young adults — built with React, React Native,
Node.js/Express, and the Anthropic Claude API.

What Is Built and Working
--------------------------

Web Application (React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS):
  - JWT authentication (signup / login / logout)
  - 7-question personalized onboarding quiz with AI-generated profile summary (Claude API)
  - Budget tracker — income/expense entry, monthly summaries, savings goals (fully functional)
  - Paper trading portfolio — buy/sell stocks with simulated prices, watchlist (fully functional)
  - SSE streaming AI chat — real-time responses from Claude with full user context injected
  - AI insight cards — 3 personalized cards per session generated by Claude (BUDGET / PORTFOLIO / MARKET)
  - Market ticker — live simulated quotes for 20+ tickers with 2-second updates
  - Banking hub — multi-account view with HYSA comparison
  - Credit cards — utilization bars, APR display, score simulator
  - Loans — avalanche vs. snowball payoff calculator
  - Roth IRA / 401K — compound growth projections, employer match optimizer
  - Savings goals — progress tracking with ETA projections
  - Fraud protection — security checklist, emergency hotlines
  - Financial education hub — 20+ courses, XP gamification, progress tracking
  - Settings — buddy name editing, subscription tier display, danger zone

Mobile Application (React Native + Expo):
  - JWT authentication with expo-secure-store token storage
  - Dashboard — live budget summary, savings goal ring, AI insight banner, recent activity
    (all data fetched from the real API — no hardcoded values)
  - Budget screen — real expense/income data from API with add-expense modal
    (grouped by category with live totals)
  - AI Chat — real SSE streaming to the backend Claude endpoint
    (text appears token-by-token as Claude generates it)
  - All 15+ screens navigable (Banking, Portfolio, Roth IRA, 401K, Savings, Loans,
    Credit Cards, Fraud Protection, Settings, Learn, Market, Expenses)

Backend (Node.js 20 + Express 5):
  - 7 REST route groups: auth, onboarding, budget, portfolio, chat, market, insights
  - JWT authentication middleware
  - SSE streaming endpoint for chat (/api/v1/chat/message)
  - Rate limiting: 200 req/15min global, 20 req/15min on auth endpoints
  - Input validation on all endpoints (enum checks, bounds checking, type guards)
  - Timing-attack-safe login (always runs bcrypt.compare)
  - In-memory Map data store with O(1) per-user secondary indexes
  - Claude API integration with graceful mock fallback when API key is absent
  - Demo user seeded on startup: demo@financebuddy.com / password123

Architecture
------------
  Client: React 18 + Vite + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + Zustand
  Mobile: React Native + Expo + Zustand
  Server: Node.js 20 + Express 5
  AI:     Anthropic Claude API (claude-sonnet-4-20250514), streaming SSE
  Auth:   JWT (7-day expiry) + bcryptjs (cost factor 10)
  State:  Zustand stores — authStore, budgetStore, portfolioStore, chatStore, marketStore

What Is Simulated (Educational Mode)
--------------------------------------
  - Stock prices: Brownian motion simulation, NOT real market data
    (Polygon.io integration is Phase 2)
  - Bank accounts: simulated balances, NOT real Plaid connections
    (Plaid integration requires legal review, Phase 3)
  - All trading is paper trading — no real money involved
  - Persistent disclaimer shown on Portfolio, Chat, and insight pages

Getting Started
---------------

Prerequisites: Node.js 20+, npm

  # Install and start the backend
  cd server
  npm install
  # Create .env with: JWT_SECRET=your_secret ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key
  npm run dev

  # Install and start the web frontend
  cd client
  npm install
  npm run dev

  # Open http://localhost:5173
  # Demo account: demo@financebuddy.com / password123

  # Mobile (requires Expo CLI)
  cd mobile
  npm install
  npx expo start

